						               													<description>Welcome to Crashbot Derby! In this board game, you play as one of 8 superpowered robots competing in the ultimate mechanized demolition derby! Attack your enemies with wild weapons, treacherous traps, or just by crashing into them! Don&amp;rsquo;t get sidetracked, though: the object is to cross the finish line first!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Gameplay&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You're in a race with up to 5 other players; your goal is to complete 3 laps (enter a checkpoint space 6 times, essentially) first. Along the way, you may step on special spaces that will give you sparks (the &amp;quot;currency&amp;quot; of this game), cards, or allow you to activate your unique Robopower!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;On your turn you may do these things:&amp;#10;- roll a 6-sided die 2 times &amp;#10;- spend sparks if you have them&amp;#10;- play cards if you have them&amp;#10;You can do these in any order. You can spend sparks &amp;#10;or play cards between die rolls.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Of course, racing is only part of it: the other part is fighting! You can attack your opponents with the cards in your hands , which usually represent a gizmo you can use offensively. You can also spend 3 red sparks to shoot opponents... and of course, as the name implies, you can crash into them!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players are never eliminated from the game, they continue racing until a winner crosses the finish line!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
